sectionText: This section is restricted to students who have a recent score on the ALEKS PPL placement exam of at least 50%.  Note that there may be a 1-day delay between completing the ALEKS PPL exam and being able to register for Math 112.  For information on taking the ALEKS PPL and dates, please see http://math.illinois.edu/ALEKS and for enrollment questions please contact mathadvising@illinois.edu <mailto:mathadvising@illinois.edu> , making sure to include your full name and 9-digit UIN. Students must register for one Lecture and one discussion section
